Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.58,0:00:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Tsunemori, take Masaoka and go look for Kougami.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.26,0:00:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a1}Kagari, Kunizuka and I will split up in order to find and destroy the source of the signal interference.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.04,0:00:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.42,0:00:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I have no idea what's going on at all.{same}
