Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.46,0:02:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with all the sneaking around?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.03,0:03:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So they're trying to ruin my fun, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.87,0:03:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.58,0:03:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.15,0:03:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}User authentication: Enforcer Kougami Shinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.18,0:03:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You are a valid user.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Target's Threat Judgment has been updated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Enforcement mode is Destroy Decomposer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.44,0:03:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Target will be completely eliminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please exercise caution.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.92,0:04:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Judging by its appearance and the pause after every second shot,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.14,0:04:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the enemy's weapon must be a double-barreled hunting rifle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.14,0:04:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, your time is up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The signal jammer has been broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.60,0:04:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon, the Bureau's main unit will rush in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.04,0:04:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Lovecraft was taken out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.44,0:04:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It was shot and destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He finally started shooting back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.98,0:04:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Senguji?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.22,0:04:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was young,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.36,0:04:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I often took part in construction work to build infrastructure in developing countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.08,0:04:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The more dangerous the place was, the more money I earned.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Conflict often broke out without warning,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and there was a limit to our ability to predict scenarios and manage risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.93,0:04:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember one time when we were attacked by guerrillas in one of those countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it was at least 70 or 80 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:05:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, my colleague who'd been sitting\N\Nright next to me was shot. Just like today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.38,0:05:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,My friend, who had been crying and\N\Nshouting just a moment earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.22,0:05:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,was reduced to nothing but a lump of flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.94,0:05:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,His blood splattered and dripped down my head,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and his smell stuck to my entire body.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to get the wrong idea, but that's actually a memory I look back on fondly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.38,0:05:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,In that moment, I felt alive... I really felt alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.26,0:05:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt it more strongly than I ever had before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.68,0:05:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I'm experiencing that feeling again right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.76,0:05:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Once again, my blood has been set alight as it pumps through this mechanical heart of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, you're telling me to run?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.26,0:05:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.22,0:05:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,From here on, it won't just be a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's exactly right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.10,0:05:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,As a hunter, I've shot down many prey over the years.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.28,0:06:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, I want to confront that man not as a hunter, but as a duelist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Makishima...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.94,0:06:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you didn't mess around with my game just to see me turn tail here, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.12,0:06:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're exactly right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll witness your life's splendor until the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.81,0:07:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be checkmate for you soon, Enforcer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.60,0:08:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Crime Coefficient is 328.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.51,0:08:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's a target for enforcement action.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.73,0:08:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing... We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We won!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry... for getting you to do something so reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.26,0:08:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you get out of here, make sure you get therapy right away.{yeah, for that DEATH FLAG}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.24,0:08:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw... too many things you shouldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay. You were wonderful, Mr. Kougami.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.56,0:09:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It almost makes me want to become a latent criminal too.{awww}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.02,0:09:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.69,0:09:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.58,0:09:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd have loved to sit here and talk with you until the crack of dawn, but you don't seem very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.76,0:09:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Until we meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.14,0:09:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kougami!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.40,0:09:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,To call this suspicious would be an understatement.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.78,0:09:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There are bullet holes all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.46,0:09:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be from a shotgun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.30,0:09:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time since I last saw traces of a gunpowder-based weapon having been used.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.02,0:09:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Masaoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.32,0:10:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Kougami...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.46,0:10:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.86,0:10:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.40,0:10:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It think it was my friend, the one who went missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.02,0:10:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Kougami?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.32,0:10:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kougami!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.56,0:10:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is terrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.50,0:10:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got quite a few bullet wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.10,0:10:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Missy! Can you administer first aid?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.30,0:10:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had a few training sessions, but I've never actually done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.76,0:10:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Then leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.06,0:10:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.79,0:10:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one more person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He took your friend away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.75,0:10:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Step aside, missy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.88,0:10:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever we do, we have to stop his bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.56,0:10:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.70,0:11:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you trying to do?! Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The case isn't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.43,0:11:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.40,0:11:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is like a battlefield... No, an execution ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.26,0:11:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It couldn't have been just three or four people...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.02,0:11:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Several dozen people... No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.56,0:11:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,At worst, close to one hundred people must have died here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.56,0:11:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Kougami was lured in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.24,0:11:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A mass murder? Why would the culprit commit such an atrocity?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.33,0:11:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he thinks it's all a game?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.22,0:11:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.98,0:11:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Er... Well, ever since we came down\N\Nhere, I've had this feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.98,0:11:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,that this place looks like the kind of battle\N\Narena you see in online action games.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.22,0:11:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I could understand if it was virtual, but playing\N\Na game using live human beings?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.14,0:11:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Hound 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.72,0:11:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Can anyone hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.32,0:11:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Shepherd 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.96,0:11:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the status over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.20,0:11:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I took Hound 3 into my care.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.00,0:11:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He's hurt so bad that I'm surprised he's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.28,0:12:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The culprit is still on the run with a hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Shepherd 2 is pursuing the culprit all by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.74,0:12:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Please hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.98,0:12:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.14,0:12:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go anywhere. We'll head over there to assist you right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,0:12:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like that damn "game" of his...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.64,0:12:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't over just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.20,0:12:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My body feels heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.50,0:12:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't feel like it belongs to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.20,0:12:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the bullets are still in your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.62,0:12:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If my hands shake while pulling them out and I hit an artery, it really will become fatal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.78,0:12:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Have the pros work on it after we get you out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.24,0:12:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Inspector Tsunemori?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.48,0:12:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'd like to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.26,0:12:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She went rushing off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.92,0:12:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It seemed like she was chasing someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.52,0:12:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done patching you up, so I'm gonna go catch up with that girl right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.36,0:12:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.29,0:12:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:12:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.10,0:12:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to do that when you're hurtin' pretty bad already.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.72,0:13:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't wanna waste any more time, injuries or no.{until narun da}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.70,0:13:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,To be frank, she's in huge danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.94,0:13:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Enforcer Masaoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.40,0:13:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Good timing! Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.18,0:13:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold down Kougami so he can't get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.46,0:13:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are tenacious, aren't you? Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.76,0:13:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.74,0:13:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like Ko shot someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.62,0:13:34.54,Psychotitle,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.62,0:13:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Senguji Toyohisa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.98,0:13:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Senguji, you said?!{nope}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.24,0:13:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you even check the Ministry of Welfare's recommended news?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.42,0:13:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I watch that crap?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.22,0:13:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:13:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Public Safety Bureau!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Drop your weapon and surrender!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.49,0:14:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Crime Coefficient is 79. Not a target for enforcement action.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The trigger will be locked.{sux}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.72,0:14:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Akane!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Just hold on, Yuki! I'll rescue you right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.94,0:14:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I've seen you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Inspector Tsunemori Akane from the Bureau, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.70,0:14:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're the one who dragged Yuki into this. How dare you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.67,0:14:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Makishima Shougo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?! Makishima?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.01,0:14:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So you know my name, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.88,0:14:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd expect no less from the Bureau.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.30,0:14:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So you guys have at least some kind of lead on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.30,0:14:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got serious charges laid against you for multiple crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.76,0:14:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,As per the Citizen's Charter, I demand that you come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.78,0:14:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If you need to talk with me, then let's do it right here, right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.56,0:14:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We're both busy people, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you can escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.88,0:14:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you should really do a better job of trying to draw me into the conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.42,0:15:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That way you can buy some time until your reinforcements arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.00,0:15:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure an experienced detective would do just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.21,0:15:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,When you said "multiple crimes," which were you referring to?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.26,0:15:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mido Masatake's? Or perhaps Ouryou Rikako's?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.18,0:15:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the only time people really have value is when they act according to their own will.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.58,0:15:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So I've asked many people about their true, repressed desires and observed their actions all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.40,0:15:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so full of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.98,0:15:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just a criminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.83,0:15:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And how do you define crime to start with?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.82,0:15:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,With the Dominator you're holding?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.26,0:15:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Does the Sibyl System that governs that gun decide it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.04,0:15:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Crime Coefficient is under 50. Not a target for enforcement action.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The trigger will be locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.90,0:15:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,By analyzing a bio-organism's force field read by a cymatic scan,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.02,0:16:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,they figure out how a person's mind works.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.96,0:16:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Science finally discovered the secret behind the human soul,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and this society changed drastically as a result.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,However, people's wills are not part of that assessment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.74,0:16:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder just what sort of criteria you use to divide people into good and evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.56,0:16:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What on Earth are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.29,0:16:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to bear witness to the splendor of man's soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.84,0:16:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to find out once and for all whether it is truly something worth admiring.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.00,0:16:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,However, when humans base their lives around Sybil's Oracle,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,without ever considering what they really want, do they really hold any value?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, while I'm here,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.14,0:16:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll try testing you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to assess your judgment and actions as a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.96,0:16:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you going to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.57,0:16:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm goin to kill this woman, Funahara Yuki...{no need to sub the gasp}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.08,0:16:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,right before your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.49,0:17:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Crime Coefficient is 48. Not a target for enforcement action.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.60,0:17:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The trigger will be locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.58,0:17:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to stop me, throw that useless piece of scrap iron aside,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.00,0:17:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,pick up the gun I just gave you, and use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.06,0:17:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If you pull the trigger, a bullet will come out.{SHIT REALLY?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.32,0:17:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-There's no way I can do that, because you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.06,0:17:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,An upstanding citizen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.92,0:17:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Sibyl decided so?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.48,0:17:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Crime Coefficient is 32. Not a target for enforcement action.{lol it's going down}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.38,0:17:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}The trigger will be locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.38,0:17:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why?!{overlap}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.15,0:17:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something I've wondered about ever since my childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,My Psycho-Pass has always been pure white.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.30,0:17:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It never got clouded in the slightest, not even once.{this seems familiar}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.82,0:17:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All sorts of vital reactions in my body must be affirming me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.80,0:17:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,thinking that my actions are those of one who is sound and good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.90,0:18:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.20,0:18:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Help! Akane!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.69,0:18:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.10,0:18:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You people can't measure my sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.52,0:18:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If anyone, the only people who'd be able to judge me are those...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.94,0:18:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,who are capable of killing based on their own will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.26,0:18:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let Yuki go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.84,0:18:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.91,0:18:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Or I'll be killed, not by a machine, but by your own intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.62,0:18:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That'd be an admirable resolution in its own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.50,0:18:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you feel the importance of life in your index finger, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.88,0:18:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's something you can never experience as one of Sibyl's puppets.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.74,0:18:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the weight of deciding something by your own free will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.10,0:18:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Crime Coefficient is under 20. Not a target for enforcement action.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.81,0:18:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The trigger will be locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.98,0:18:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Descartes said that those who are unable to make a decision
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.78,0:19:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,can't do so because either their desires are too great, or because they lack intellect.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.78,0:19:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? If you don't hold the gun steady, you'll miss me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.20,0:19:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, aim at me with killing intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.54,0:19:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Akane...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.52,0:19:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How regrettable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.12,0:19:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How very regrettable, Inspector Tsunemori Akane.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.10,0:19:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.84,0:19:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.95,0:19:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Akane!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.70,0:19:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You've disappointed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.08,0:19:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll have to punish you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.42,0:19:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.72,0:19:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.08,0:19:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Regret your helplessness, and despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.84,0:20:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Crime Coefficient is 0. Not a target for enforcement action.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.09,0:20:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}The trigger will be locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.32,0:20:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!{overlap}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.56,0:20:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Missy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.54,0:20:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You've come to?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.71,0:20:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Inspector Tsunemori?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.72,0:20:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I just stood there and let Yuki die...{nice suicide blanket}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.18,0:20:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I just stood there and let Yuki die...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.20,0:21:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.78,0:21:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I met...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.40,0:21:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.33,0:21:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That man?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.76,0:21:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Makishima Shougo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.28,0:21:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dominators...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.24,0:21:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,can't judge him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.46,0:21:26.39,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,2200)\blur1}It seems all fairy tales {\alpha&HFF&}are dead
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.65,0:21:30.37,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,900)\blur1\alpha&HFF&}It seems {\alpha&H00&}all fairy tales are dead
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.12,0:21:35.72,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,900)\blur1}In a hospital ward of brick stones
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.58,0:21:40.81,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,900)\blur1}my voice is too coarse to sing
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.80,0:21:45.93,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,900)\blur1}Outside in the foggy haze
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.14,0:21:51.53,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,900)\blur1}a red moon glows
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.48,0:21:56.93,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,900)\blur1}Look at me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.75,0:22:02.45,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,900)\blur1}Do not avert your gaze
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.83,0:22:06.77,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}Behind black bars
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.57,0:22:09.45,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}I was born
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.25,0:22:11.89,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}I wish there were a punishment for evil
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.69,0:22:14.76,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}Always I need you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.56,0:22:17.43,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}Now, grant us justice
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.23,0:22:19.95,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}before chaos takes us all
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.67,0:22:25.40,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}Pay the price of fate and be rewarded, nameless beast
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.24,0:22:28.16,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}Black rain falls from the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.00,0:22:30.75,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}and I remain forever unwanted
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.59,0:22:33.58,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}My crazed neurosis
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.42,0:22:36.23,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}pulls me towards the sinful hellfire
Dialogue: 1,0:22:36.07,0:22:38.80,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}Now, mete out justice
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.64,0:22:41.43,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}Even my ever-bleeding wounds shall be my friend
Dialogue: 1,0:22:41.27,0:22:46.66,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}Let's accept who we are and walk together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.50,0:22:51.67,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,1000)\blur1}We, who are nameless beasts
